TypeScript is a typed superset of JavaScript that compiles to plain JavaScript. This is a list of TypeScript types generated from the declaration files for react, react-dom, and react-native in https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/tree/c807902. The script to generate this list is on github. Fixes welcome. See also my TypeScript cheat sheet, and Docker cheat sheet.
